{"data":[{"date":"16:58 02/07","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u00e0 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn M.U chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 3","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/8/nguoi-nha-xac-nhan-mu-chuan-bi-co-tan-binh-thu-3.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn t\u1eeb nhi\u1ebfp \u1ea3nh gia Craig Norwood, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Lee Grant chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nM.U s\u1eafp c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 3<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tranh th\u1ee7 th\u1eddi gian c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n tham d\u1ef1 World Cup, Jose Mourinho v\u00e0 BL\u0110 Man United \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm ch\u1ed1t t\u00e2n binh m\u1edbi. Theo \u0111\u00f3, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng bom t\u1ea5n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n, m\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd \u0111em v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Lee Grant \u2013 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ef1 do, sau khi h\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Stoke.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u0103m nay 35 tu\u1ed5i, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh sinh ra t\u1ea1i Anh n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 3 t\u1ea1i Old Trafford \u2013 sau David De Gea v\u00e0 Sergio Romero. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n cho r\u1eb1ng Grant s\u1ebd thay th\u1ebf De Gea ra \u0111i c\u0169ng s\u1edbm b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf, khi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh T\u00e2y Ban Nha chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a, M.U s\u1ebd g\u1eedi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Joel Pereira cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00edch l\u0169y kinh nghi\u1ec7m. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 21 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh cho m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh v\u1edbi 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh, b\u1edfi v\u1eady anh mu\u1ed1n CLB cho m\u00ecnh \u0111i \u201cdu h\u1ecdc\u201d. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, M.U c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, n\u00ean h\u1ecd s\u1ebd th\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea3o g\u1eedi anh sang \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi \u0111em v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u00e0 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Lee Grant h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u00e0 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Lee Grant h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/Nguoi-nha-xac-nhan-MU-chieu-mo-Lee-Grant-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Lee Grant chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>\u00a0</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn t\u1eeb nhi\u1ebfp \u1ea3nh gia Craig Norwood, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t ng\u00f4n vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a CLB \u2013 \u0111\u00e3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee5p h\u00ecnh Lee Grant trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o m\u1edbi. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Norwood \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 2 t\u00e2n binh Fred v\u00e0 Diogo Dalot \u2013 ch\u1ec9 1 ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi CLB \u0111\u01b0a ra th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi chi\u1ec1u cao 1m93 v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m chinh chi\u1ebfn \u1edf gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 35 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p cho Man United. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3i qua l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau, v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Romero \u0111\u1ebfn nay v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Lee Grant, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111em v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, h\u1ecd \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Adrien Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/mot-doi-bong-tu-choi-co-hoi-chieu-mo-pogba-serbia-176-190157.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/16/mot-doi-bong-tu-choi-co-hoi-chieu-mo-pogba-serbia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/mot-doi-bong-tu-choi-co-hoi-chieu-mo-pogba-serbia-176-190157.html\">M\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Pogba Serbia</span><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Juventus mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00e1n ng\u1ea5y v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi t\u1eeb Lazio.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-ben-do-moi-cua-martial-neu-roi-mu-172-190097.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/14/day-ben-do-moi-cua-martial-neu-roi-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-ben-do-moi-cua-martial-neu-roi-mu-172-190097.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! B\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Martial n\u1ebfu r\u1eddi MU?</span><br>\r\nBayern Munich mu\u1ed1n mua Anthony Martial, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p r\u1eddi Old Trafford nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ng\u00f4i sao...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-muon-gay-soc-vu-muc-tieu-hang-dau-cua-liverpool-172-190006.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/29/mu-muon-gay-soc-vu-muc-tieu-hang-dau-cua-liverpool.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-muon-gay-soc-vu-muc-tieu-hang-dau-cua-liverpool-172-190006.html\">MU mu\u1ed1n g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1ee5 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Liverpool</span><br>\r\nMU mu\u1ed1n mua Nabil Fekir, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018. \u0110\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t The Kop, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi \u0111\u1ee7 66 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"821","checkdouble":"190176"},{"date":"16:13 02/07","title":"Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng cho c\u1ea7u \u0111inh Brazil vs Mexico","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/nhan-dinh-brazil-vs-mexico-va-du-doan-soi-keo-mexico-vs-brazil.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs Mexico kh\u00f4ng ai ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u nh\u00e0m ch\u00e1n. Phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn d\u00f9 theo nh\u1eefng phong c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c nhau.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- <strong>Nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</strong> (\u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3)<br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: Brazil th\u1eafng 2-1<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u: Brazil vs Mexico<br>\r\nTh\u1eddi gian: 21h ng\u00e0y 2/7<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m: S\u00e2n Samara Arena<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTLCA c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: Brazil 0.87*0:1*-0.92 Mexico<br>\r\nTBT c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: Nhi\u1ec1u 0.96*2 1/2*0.97 \u00cdt<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs Mexico v\u00e0 d\u01b0 \u0111o\u00e1n, soi k\u00e8o, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs Mexico v\u00e0 d\u01b0 \u0111o\u00e1n, soi k\u00e8o, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/nhan-dinh-brazil-vs-mexico-va-du-doan-soi-keo-mexico-vs-brazil.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs Mexico 21h ng\u00e0y 2/7</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi Brazil, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt g\u00ec kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. L\u00fd do HLV Dunga b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 n\u1eb1m \u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00edch m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u1edf c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng. Tite l\u00ean nh\u1eadm ch\u1ee9c thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 r\u00fat ra kinh nghi\u1ec7m s\u00e2u s\u1eafc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 t\u00ednh to\u00e1n t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2u, Tite c\u0169ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00fap Brazil ghi th\u1eadt nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. T\u00ednh t\u1edbi nay, sau 24 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Selecao, \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh 19 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng (t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 79,17%), ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edbi 52 b\u00e0n (trung b\u00ecnh 2,1 b\u00e0n/ tr\u1eadn).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Brazil nhe nhang vuot qua Serbia\" title=\"Brazil nhe nhang vuot qua Serbia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/thay-gi-trong-ngay-brazil-nhe-nhang-ha-serbia-20.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Brazil c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBrazil kh\u00f4ng khi n\u00e0o thi\u1ebfu nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao v\u00e0 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 c\u0169ng v\u1eady. T\u1eeb Neymar, Coutinho t\u1edbi Jesus, Willian r\u1ed3i Douglas Costa, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn trong nh\u1eefng pha x\u1eed l\u00fd c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. 7 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua c\u1ea3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 giao h\u1eefu, c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 5 l\u00e0 h\u1ecd ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ef1 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a Brazil l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i b\u00e0n c\u00e3i. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs Mexico kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 nh\u00ecn v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ph\u00eda. Mexico s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 m\u0169 r\u1ed9ng v\u00e0nh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng t\u1eed th\u1ee7 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/giai-ma-mexico-tai-world-cup-2018-qua-nhanh-qua-nguy-hiem-466-189773.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/giai-ma-mexico-tai-world-cup-2018-qua-nhanh-qua-nguy-hiem.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/giai-ma-mexico-tai-world-cup-2018-qua-nhanh-qua-nguy-hiem-466-189773.html\">Gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 Mexico t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018: Qu\u00e1 nhanh, qu\u00e1 nguy hi\u1ec3m</span><br>\r\n<span>T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean Mexico c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i r\u00ecnh r\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea7y nguy...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e3y nh\u00ecn chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Mexico tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c. 42% th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u00f3ng l\u0103n l\u00e0 b\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Mexico nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 b\u00ean c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c. C\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i nh\u01b0ng li\u00ean t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee3t ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u00f2n c\u1ee7a Mexico.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Osorio tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00f4i c\u00f4ng s\u00f2ng ph\u1eb3ng c\u00f9ng \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 sau c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1eef \u0111\u00fang l\u1eddi h\u1ee9a. Mexico l\u00f9i s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 nh\u01b0ng lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 3 m\u0169i c\u00f4ng \u1edf ph\u00eda tr\u00ean bao g\u1ed3m Hirving Lozano, Carlos Vela v\u00e0 Chicharito.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Mexico tai World Cup 2018 dang co nhung don tan cong chop nhoang ma ban thang cua Lozano la vi du dien hinh.\" title=\"\u0110T Mexico t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f2n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ch\u1edbp nho\u00e1ng m\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Lozano l\u00e0 v\u00ed d\u1ee5 \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/mexico-6.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mexico ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 khoa h\u1ecdc</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tho\u00e1t pressing c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, Mexico lu\u00f4n bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi ch\u00e2n c\u00e1c m\u0169i c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng El Tri c\u00f3 2, 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean ti\u1ec1n tuy\u1ebfn \u00e1p s\u00e1t c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c. N\u1ebfu h\u1ecd ch\u1eaft chiu h\u01a1n trong nh\u1eefng pha x\u1eed l\u00fd sau c\u00f9ng, s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n thua c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n con s\u1ed1 1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n tr\u00ean s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mexico t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil. Hai c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 n\u01a1i t\u1ed1t l\u00e0nh cho El Tri khai th\u00e1c. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/da-co-ket-luan-ve-kha-nang-da-chinh-cua-marcelo-truoc-mexico-421-190145.html\" target=\"_blank\">Marcelo ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n do ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</span> trong khi th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Danilo c\u00f2n l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Marcelo roi san som do chan thuong\" title=\"Marcelo roi san som do chan thuong\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Truoc-tran-gap-Mexico,-HLV-Tite-phat-bieu-ve-Marcelo-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Marcelo v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi do ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, Filipe Luis v\u00e0 Fagner s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn 2 c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a Brazil. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb, nh\u01b0ng thi\u1ebfu kinh nghi\u1ec7m qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u1ee9 2. \u0110\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng r\u1ee7i ro x\u1ea3y ra, Brazil bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i l\u1ea5y c\u00f4ng b\u00f9 th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs Mexico kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i s\u1edbm \u1edf World Cup 2018 c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 b\u1edfi h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Nh\u01b0ng Brazil v\u1edbi h\u1ecfa l\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu b\u00f3 tay tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBrazil s\u1ebd nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-3 c\u1ee7a Mexico tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 r\u00fat ra nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc cho m\u00ecnh. Nh\u1eefng pha t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng tr\u1ef1c di\u1ec7n, nhanh ch\u00f3ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng 5 l\u1ea7n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Link xem truc tiep Brazil vs Mexico\" title=\"Link xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Brazil vs Mexico\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/link-xem-brazil-vs-mexico.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">90 ph\u00fat tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Samara Arena s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Tite c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 khoan ph\u00e1 \u201cb\u00ea t\u00f4ng\u201d. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u01b0\u1eddi, Brazil c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eeb xa c\u1ee7a Willian, Coutinho. C\u0169ng ch\u00ednh h\u1ecd c\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi Neymar s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nR\u1ed3i v\u1ec1 kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn, Brazil \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Paulinho r\u1ed3i c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 Miranda, Thiago Silva s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tham chi\u1ebfn. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean s\u1eb5n \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong t\u1eebng tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00e1c nhau. M\u1ed9t \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u1ed1 1 cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u201cqu\u00e2n b\u00e0i trong tay \u00e1o\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil vs Mexico h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng thi\u1ebfu b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. M\u1ed1c 2,5 b\u00e0n m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng m\u00e0 gi\u1edbi d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u1eb7t ra \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n b\u1ecb ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018. Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Samara Arena t\u1ed1i nay, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- <strong>Nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</strong> (\u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3)<br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: Brazil th\u1eafng 2-1<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t kh\u00e1c:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- T\u1ed5ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 l\u1ebb<br>\r\n- Mexico kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi<br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 10 (O 9 1/2)<br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c hi\u1ec7p 1 c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 5 (O 4 1/2)<br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 4 (O 4)<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Brazil nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 (-2 1/2)<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c hi\u1ec7p 1 c\u1ee7a Brazil nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 (-1 1/4)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ea3i Ly (TTVN)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"820","checkdouble":"190178"},{"date":"16:56 02/07","title":"Salah gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p t\u1eeb Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/13/hlv-klopp-phat-bieu-ve-viec-salah-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Jeremie Aliadiere kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Pogba v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n t\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi l\u00e0 v\u00ec Mourinho.</h2><h2>Pogba ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man United \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng khi \u0111\u01b0a Pogba tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford h\u00e8 2016. Sau 4 n\u0103m thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i Juventus, Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t gi\u00fap Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf l\u00e0m m\u01b0a l\u00e0m gi\u00f3 t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e2y gi\u1edd v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a x\u1ea3y ra.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/pogba-len-tieng-dap-tra-nhung-chi-trich-172-187755.html\" target=\"_blank\">ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch</span>. Anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Mournho v\u00e0 c\u0169ng nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho \u0111ang k\u00ecm h\u00e3m Pogba \u1edf MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mourinho \u0111ang k\u00ecm h\u00e3m Pogba \u1edf MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Mourinho-dang-kim-ham-Pogba-o-MU-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Aliadiere cho r\u1eb1ng Mourinho \u0111ang k\u00ecm h\u00e3m Pogba</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Aliadiere \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 l\u00fd do d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n thi\u1ebfu \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Pogba trong th\u1eddi gian qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cTh\u1eadt kh\u00f3 cho Pogba khi HLV kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n. V\u00e0 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng v\u00e0 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n su\u1ed1t c\u1ea3 n\u0103m tr\u1eddi. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u00e1i ki\u1ec3u \u2018t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 su\u1ed1t m\u00f9a \u1edf Man United nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf World Cup 2018 cho Ph\u00e1p\u2019.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i nh\u1edb khi Pogba \u1edf Juventus, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi gia nh\u1eadp Man United, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c Mourinho kh\u00f4ng trao cho Pogba nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n t\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao h\u01a1n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 duy tr\u00ec vi\u1ec7c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01a1n\u201d.</em><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Pogba m\u1ea5t gi\u00e1 \u1edf tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a Pogba trong l\u00f2ng NHM Man United c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ee5t gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. S\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh khi\u1ebfn anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cC\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i tr\u1eadn, Pogba mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u1ea1i t\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p g\u00ec\u201d, Aliadiere n\u00f3i th\u00eam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cB\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn 100% s\u1ee9c l\u1ef1c. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina nh\u1edd t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i xung quanh ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng khi ch\u00fang ta th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n Pogba, c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng l\u00ean tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean nhanh ch\u00f3ng th\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u1edf \u0111\u00f3 n\u1eefa\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Pogba:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/pogba-tang-boc-mbappe-len-may-sau-tran-dai-thang-argentina-469-190086.html\">Pogba th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng b\u1eb1ng Mbappe</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/pogba-phan-phao-truoc-nhung-chi-trich-cua-cdv-phap-469-189872.html\">Pogba ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u1ee7a C\u0110V Ph\u00e1p</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"819","checkdouble":"190179"},{"date":"16:55 02/07","title":"Danny Welbeck ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft l\u00e0m b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/danny-welbeck-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-lam-ban-cua-dt-anh-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Danny Welbeck mu\u1ed1n \u0110T Anh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 tr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Colombia t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng b\u00f3ng ch\u1ebft<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup, \u0110T Anh n\u1eb1m trong nh\u00f3m 3 \u0111\u1ed9i ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t (8), b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi Nga v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 k\u00e9m B\u1ec9 (9). \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd l\u00e0 Tam S\u01b0 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh khi c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 6 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng &quot;b\u00f3ng ch\u1ebft&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Danny Welbeck muon DT Anh tan dung bong chet tai World Cup 2018.\" title=\"Danny Welbeck mu\u1ed1n \u0110T Anh t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng b\u00f3ng ch\u1ebft t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/danny-welbeck-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-lam-ban-cua-dt-anh-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Danny Welbeck mu\u1ed1n \u0110T Anh t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng b\u00f3ng ch\u1ebft t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o nguy hi\u1ec3m cho Colombia khi hai \u0111\u1ed9i g\u1eb7p nhau \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i. T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, c\u1ea3 hai b\u00e0n thua c\u1ee7a Colombia \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n khi b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eeb s\u1edbm, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng pha &quot;b\u00f3ng ch\u1ebft&quot;.</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Welbeck mu\u1ed1n t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng b\u00f3ng ch\u1ebft<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Colombia, Danny Welbeck mu\u1ed1n \u0110T Anh t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng b\u00f3ng ch\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m b\u00e0n: &quot;V\u1edbi c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean mu\u1ed1n t\u1ea1o ra th\u1eadt nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. C\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;T\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf c\u00e1c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nguy hi\u1ec3m. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n t\u1eeb b\u00f3ng s\u1ed1ng&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Danny Welbeck c\u0169ng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 r\u1eb1ng Tam S\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e2n t\u00edch r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Colombia: &quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ph\u00e2n t\u00edch th\u1eadt k\u1ef9. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 y\u1ebfu n\u00ean s\u1ebd d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 khai th\u00e1c. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Colombia vs Anh s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 1h00 ng\u00e0y 4/7.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sao-arsenal-len-tieng-de-doa-dt-anh-421-190170.html\">Sao Arsenal l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111e d\u1ecda \u0110T Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dele-alli-noi-cung-truoc-tran-gap-colombia-421-190166.html\">Dele Alli n\u00f3i c\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Colombia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/lingard-phat-bieu-ve-dt-anh-tai-world-cup-2018-421-190149.html\">Lingard ch\u1ec9 ra l\u00fd do \u0110T Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/colombia-co-noi-gian-trong-doi-tuyen-anh-421-190124.html\">Colombia c\u00f3 &ldquo;n\u1ed9i gi\u00e1n&rdquo; trong \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/doi-tuyen-anh-san-sang-pha-dop-luan-luu-11m-421-190119.html\">\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ph\u00e1 d\u1edbp lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/rooney-doi-tuyen-anh-se-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-469-190108.html\">Rooney: \u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh s\u1ebd v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N.D (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"818","checkdouble":"190181"},{"date":"16:43 02/07","title":"D\u01b0 \u00e2m v\u00f2ng 17 V-League: H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfn s\u00e1t ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng, HAGL chia \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/du-am-vong-17-vleague-ha-noi-tien-sat-ngoi-vuong-hagl-chia-diem-dang-tiec.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, HAGL ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a \u1edf v\u00f2ng 17 V-League.</h2><h2>1. H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i b\u0103ng b\u0103ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf khi ph\u1ea3i di chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi s\u00e2n C\u1ea9m Ph\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh tuy nhi\u00ean H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i lu\u00f4n bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng sau 17 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1edbm sau pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a ngo\u1ea1i binh Vinicius \u1edf ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 8 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0ng b\u1eb1ng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm t\u00e1i l\u1eadp th\u1ebf c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng sau c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Ph\u1ea1m Th\u00e0nh L\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf ph\u00fat 31. 5 ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 V\u0103n Ki\u00ean \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 duy tr\u00ec t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1 t\u1edbi h\u1ebft tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m ngay t\u1ea1i C\u1ea9m Ph\u1ea3, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc \u1edf ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi 44 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp sau l\u00e0 Sanna Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a BVN \u0111\u1ebfn 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m, m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch qu\u00e1 an to\u00e0n cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh chinh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m v\u00f2ng 17 V-League H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfn s\u00e1t ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng, HAGL chia \u0111i\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m v\u00f2ng 17 V-League H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfn s\u00e1t ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng, HAGL chia \u0111i\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/a00-8311-1530455756.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch tr\u01b0\u1edbc 5 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>2. HAGL b\u1ecb c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 17 V-League, CLB HAGL c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Tam K\u1ef3 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang gi\u1eef ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch l\u00e0 CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Nam. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t Qu\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Claudecir kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, HAGL \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn kh\u00e1 l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n To\u00e0n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean b\u01b0\u1edbc sang hi\u1ec7p 2, khi th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i xu\u1ed1ng, &lsquo;G\u1ed7&rsquo; \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea1i th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 ghi li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng v\u00e0i ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 2-2. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u khi\u1ebfn HAGL \u0111\u00e1nh r\u01a1i 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7y ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi Tam K\u1ef3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00f2a tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, CLB HAGL&nbsp;v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f2i l\u1ea1i m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua Qu\u1ea3ng Nam tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Pleiku \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 5 tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng v\u1edbi 24 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>3. SLNA l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ed1p 6<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 5 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, CLB SLNA kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi nh\u00f3m c\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecf m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111ang s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u1ea1nh tranh t\u1ed1p 3 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i V-League 2018. T\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn sau v\u00f2ng 17 V-League, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 23 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 k\u00e9m v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a \u0111\u00fang 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec m\u1ea1ch tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, SLNA ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u01a1 t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n tr\u00ean BXH tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i k\u1ebft th\u00fac. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">SLNA thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong th\u1eddi gian qua c\u0169ng nh\u1edd v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c. Sau hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i L\u1ea1ch Tray b\u1eb1ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e2ng t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean th\u00e0nh 3-0&nbsp;\u1edf ph\u00fat 69 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i chung cu\u1ed9c 3-2 trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i L\u1ea1ch Tray.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 ghi b\u00e0n n\u00e0y, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hai Phong vs SLNA\" title=\"H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng vs SLNA\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/nhan-dinh-hai-phong-vs-slna-17h00-ngay-17-vleague-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>SLNA \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng t\u1ea1i L\u1ea1ch Tray</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>4. S\u00e0i G\u00f2n khi\u1ebfn cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng th\u00eam c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 s\u00edt sao 1-0 nh\u1edd b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb Thanh H\u00f3a L\u00ea Qu\u1ed1c Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 90 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap S\u00e0i G\u00f2n t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u00ean BXH m\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, n\u00f3 c\u00f2n t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u00eam quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a CLB tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng an to\u00e0n. L\u00fac n\u00e0y S\u00e0i G\u00f2n c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 h\u01a1n TP.HCM 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1eabu bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng s\u1eafp t\u1edbi v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu duy tr\u00ec m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u1edf l\u1ea1i V-League m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng 2019.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/1/Highlight-Quang-Ninh-vs-Ha-Noi.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BXH sau vong 17 V-League 2018\" title=\"BXH sau v\u00f2ng 17 V-League 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/BXH-sau-vong-17-V-League-2018.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>BXH sau v\u00f2ng 17 V-League 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/diem-nhan-quang-nam-22-hagl-cu-dup-cua-van-toan-168-190109.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/van-toan-ghi-ban.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/diem-nhan-quang-nam-22-hagl-cu-dup-cua-van-toan-168-190109.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Qu\u1ea3ng Nam 2-2 HAGL: C\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n To\u00e0n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam \u1edf v\u00f2ng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-tiec-nuoi-sau-tran-hoa-cua-hagl-truoc-quang-nam-168-190172.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-tiec-nuoi-sau-tran-hoa-cua-hagl-truoc-quang-nam.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-tiec-nuoi-sau-tran-hoa-cua-hagl-truoc-quang-nam-168-190172.html\">HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a HAGL tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m d\u00f9 h\u1ecd m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/de-thua-tuong-moi-cua-sai-gon-hlv-nam-dinh-noi-gi-168-190140.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/de-thua-tuong-moi-cua-sai-gon-hlv-nam-dinh-noi-gi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/de-thua-tuong-moi-cua-sai-gon-hlv-nam-dinh-noi-gi-168-190140.html\">\u0110\u1ec3 thua t\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, HLV Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng CLB Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u0129 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"817","checkdouble":"190182"},{"date":"17:30 02/07","title":"\"Mourinho \u0111ang ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Pogba v\u01b0\u01a1n t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec9nh cao\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/23/mourinho-dang-ngan-can-pogba-vuon-toi-dinh-cao.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Jeremie Aliadiere kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Pogba v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n t\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi l\u00e0 v\u00ec Mourinho.</h2><h2>Pogba ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man United \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng khi \u0111\u01b0a Pogba tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford h\u00e8 2016. Sau 4 n\u0103m thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i Juventus, Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t gi\u00fap Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf l\u00e0m m\u01b0a l\u00e0m gi\u00f3 t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e2y gi\u1edd v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a x\u1ea3y ra.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/pogba-len-tieng-dap-tra-nhung-chi-trich-172-187755.html\" target=\"_blank\">ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch</span>. Anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Mournho v\u00e0 c\u0169ng nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho \u0111ang k\u00ecm h\u00e3m Pogba \u1edf MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mourinho \u0111ang k\u00ecm h\u00e3m Pogba \u1edf MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Mourinho-dang-kim-ham-Pogba-o-MU-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Aliadiere cho r\u1eb1ng Mourinho \u0111ang k\u00ecm h\u00e3m Pogba</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Aliadiere \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 l\u00fd do d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n thi\u1ebfu \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Pogba trong th\u1eddi gian qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cTh\u1eadt kh\u00f3 cho Pogba khi HLV kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n. V\u00e0 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng v\u00e0 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n su\u1ed1t c\u1ea3 n\u0103m tr\u1eddi. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u00e1i ki\u1ec3u \u2018t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 su\u1ed1t m\u00f9a \u1edf Man United nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf World Cup 2018 cho Ph\u00e1p\u2019.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i nh\u1edb khi Pogba \u1edf Juventus, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi gia nh\u1eadp Man United, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c Mourinho kh\u00f4ng trao cho Pogba nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n t\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao h\u01a1n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 duy tr\u00ec vi\u1ec7c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01a1n\u201d.</em><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Pogba m\u1ea5t gi\u00e1 \u1edf tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a Pogba trong l\u00f2ng NHM Man United c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ee5t gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. S\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh khi\u1ebfn anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cC\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i tr\u1eadn, Pogba mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u1ea1i t\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p g\u00ec\u201d, Aliadiere n\u00f3i th\u00eam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cB\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn 100% s\u1ee9c l\u1ef1c. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina nh\u1edd t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i xung quanh ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng khi ch\u00fang ta th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n Pogba, c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng l\u00ean tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean nhanh ch\u00f3ng th\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u1edf \u0111\u00f3 n\u1eefa\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Pogba:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/pogba-tang-boc-mbappe-len-may-sau-tran-dai-thang-argentina-469-190086.html\">Pogba th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng b\u1eb1ng Mbappe</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/pogba-phan-phao-truoc-nhung-chi-trich-cua-cdv-phap-469-189872.html\">Pogba ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u1ee7a C\u0110V Ph\u00e1p</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"816","checkdouble":"190183"},{"date":"17:46 02/07","title":"HLV Mexico lo s\u1ee3 t\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Brazil","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/mon-nghe-thuat-thu-tam.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Juan Carlos Osorio kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Mexico \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi l\u00e0 Brazil \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</h2><h2>Osorio e ng\u1ea1i Brazil</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Osorio hi\u1ec3u kh\u00e1 r\u00f5 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Brazil. \u00d4ng t\u1eebng n\u1eafm quy\u1ec1n \u1edf Sao Paulo tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00ean d\u1eabn d\u1eaft El Tri. V\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-brazil-vs-mexico-va-du-doan-soi-keo-mexico-vs-brazil-421-190178.html\" target=\"_blank\">Mexico vs Brazil</span> s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, Osorio kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea7n ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen v\u1ec1 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Selecao hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Mexico lo s\u1ee3 t\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Brazil vs Mexico h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Mexico lo s\u1ee3 t\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Brazil vs Mexico h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/mon-nghe-thuat-thu-tam.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV\u00a0Osorio e ng\u1ea1i Brazil</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Brazil l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng d\u00e1m n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh t\u1eadp th\u1ec3, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1edf h\u1eefu kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 theo b\u1ea3n n\u0103ng nh\u01b0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cH\u1ecd c\u00f3 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao. N\u1ebfu c\u1ea3 Neymar, Willian, Coutinho, Gabriel Jesus v\u00e0 Douglas Costa c\u00f9ng \u1edf tr\u00ean s\u00e2n th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 con s\u1ed1 5. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t si\u00eau \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. Trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd th\u00ec tranh b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng t\u1ed1t trong khi c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh tham gia t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t t\u1edbi n\u1ed7i kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o s\u00e1nh b\u1eb1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTite c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t HLV \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch g\u1eafn k\u1ebft c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Fernandinho v\u00e0 Casemiro. V\u1eady n\u00ean t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Mexico s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t. N\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u0111\u00e1ng xem\u201d.</em><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mexico quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 t\u1ecf ra e ng\u1ea1i s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Brazil nh\u01b0ng HLV Osorio kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. <br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201c\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng khi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh lui v\u1ec1 v\u00e0 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 cho kh\u00e2u ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng khi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u00ecn chung, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng t\u1eed th\u1ee7. Brazil c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t. T\u1eed th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u1ef1 s\u00e1t, gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1eebng ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u1edbi h\u1ecd tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Mexico vs Brazil:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-brazil-vs-mexico-21h-ngay-27-cho-doi-tran-cau-kinh-dien-421-190148.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs Mexico (21h ng\u00e0y 2/7): Ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-brazil-vs-mexico-va-du-doan-soi-keo-mexico-vs-brazil-421-190178.html\">Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng cho c\u1ea7u \u0111inh Brazil vs Mexico</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"815","checkdouble":"190186"},{"date":"17:40 02/07","title":"Rashford: \"N\u1ebfu Anh ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 11m t\u00f4i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng nh\u1eadn tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/rashford-neu-anh-phai-da-11m-toi-san-sang-nhan-trach-nhiem.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Marcus Rashford ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1 11m khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV y\u00eau c\u1ea7u.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh \u0111ang t\u1eadp s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac theo m\u1ed9t k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n. Nga h\u00f2a TBN 1-1 sau 120 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 4-3 tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.<br />\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Marcus Rashford ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Marcus Rashford ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/rashford-neu-anh-phai-da-11m-toi-san-sang-nhan-trach-nhiem.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Marcus Rashford ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Anh \u0111ang t\u1eadp \u0111\u00e1 11m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-croatia-vs-dan-mach-463-190116.html\" target=\"_blank\">Croatia v\u00e0 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch</span> c\u0169ng k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a 1-1 sau 120 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u, \u1edf lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u00e1 11m \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 3-2.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u0169ng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u1eadp s\u00fat 11m.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nAnh v\u00e0 Colombia l\u00e0 c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 11m \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft th\u1eafng thua l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra. Rashford ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Tam s\u01b0 \u0111ang t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u1eadp \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Colombia \u0111ang t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u1eadp s\u00fat lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u, Anh c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0m v\u1eady. B\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n n\u00e0o c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng trong m\u1ecdi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Rashford s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1 11m</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Marcus Rashford ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1 11m khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV y\u00eau c\u1ea7u.<br />\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"rashford anh bi\" title=\"rashford anh b\u1ec9\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/Thong-ke-Anh-vs-Bi---Bang-G-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rashford s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1 11m khi c\u1ea7n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n\u201cTrong m\u00e0u \u00e1o M.U t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 11m, trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Anh t\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u t\u00f4i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng nh\u1eadn nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ki\u1ec3m ch\u1ee9ng b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c, t\u00f4i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1 11m khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u. Gareth Southgate bi\u1ebft nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ef1 tin trong ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u00f3, t\u00f4i tin v\u00e0o quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1 11m c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1ea5y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"814","checkdouble":"190189"},{"date":"17:22 02/07","title":"3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a TBN tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nga","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-4-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-thua-cua-tbn-truoc-nga.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua Nga 3-4 tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m qua \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Nga v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Igor Akinfeev</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nIgor Akinfeev l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Nga \u1edf World Cup 2018, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00ed nh\u01b0 &ldquo;Lev Yashin \u0111\u1ec7 nh\u1ecb&rdquo; \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00e0 t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Nga v\u00f2ng 18 World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Nga v\u00f2ng 18 World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/Diem-nhan-Tay-Ban-Nha-vs-Nga-vong-18-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Igor Akinfeev c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 32 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i tuy\u1ec7t hay \u1edf tr\u1eadn T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Nga v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018. Trong 120 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh sinh n\u0103m 1986 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 8 pha c\u1ee9u thua, b\u00e0n thua duy nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 Nga ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ee9u thua xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a Akinfeev l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Nga bu\u1ed9c T\u00e2y Ban Nha ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 11m \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m penalty c\u00e2n n\u00e3o th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 32 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o CSKA Moscow \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Koke v\u00e0 Iago Aspas, qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap Nga \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha 4-3 tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 32 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang Whoscored ch\u1ea5m \u0111i\u1ec3m cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua cu\u1ed9c: Sergei Ignashevich</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sergei Ignashevich ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 gi\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 ngay ph\u00fat 12, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 38 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u1ec1 l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng tranh ch\u1ea5p v\u1edbi Sergio Ramos.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tinh huong Sergei Ignashevich phan luoi nha\" title=\"T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Sergei Ignashevich ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/pan-luoi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Sergei Ignashevich ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Ignashevich \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t huy tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 tinh qu\u00e1i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i b\u00ean ph\u00eda T\u00e2y Ban Nha. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 pha ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 th\u1ee9 10 \u1edf World Cup 2018, m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed1t l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 38 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f2n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng di chuy\u1ec3n, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 Ignashevich trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nIgnashevich \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i David de Gea \u1edf lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u00e1 11m, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3 anh s\u1ebd b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Nga s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Croatia \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro s\u1ebd khai th\u00e1c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 38 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Artem Dzyuba</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Fedor Smolov l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 1 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Nga \u1edf World Cup 2018, tuy nhi\u00ean c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb sau phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c cao c\u1ee7a Artem Dzyuba.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Artem Dzyuba dang choi rat an tuong\" title=\"Artem Dzyuba \u0111ang ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/zuba.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Artem Dzyuba \u0111ang ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Saudi Arabia, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, anh ghi 1 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o ch\u1ec9 sau 20 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u00ednh m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap Dzyuba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a Nga, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1988 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn HLV Stanislav Cherchesov ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArtem Dzyuba ghi 1 b\u00e0n trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-1 c\u1ee7a Nga tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ai C\u1eadp, \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha anh c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1 cho Nga b\u1eb1ng c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m. T\u00ednh ra ng\u00f4i sao 28 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 b\u00e0n c\u00f9ng 1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u1edf World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Artem Dzyuba s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Croatia, c\u00e1i duy\u00ean ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n \u1edf World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua cu\u1ed9c: Gerard Pique</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gerard Pique \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nga, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Artem Dzyuba l\u00e0m kh\u1ed5.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gerard Pique de bong cham tay trong vong cam\" title=\"Gerard Pique \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea1m tay trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/pique.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Gerard Pique \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea1m tay trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Barca ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea1m tay trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m gi\u00fap Nga \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng 11m v\u00e0 Dzyuba kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nga, nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng Pique c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn. Anh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi Ronaldo gi\u00fap CR7 c\u00f3 c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t m\u1eabu m\u1ef1c mang v\u1ec1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a 3-3 cho B\u0110N tr\u01b0\u1edbc TBN.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi 6 b\u00e0n sau 4 tr\u1eadn \u1edf World Cup 2018, vi\u1ec7c Pique ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn khung th\u00e0nh David de Gea th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Mario Fernandes</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mario Fernandes chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho CSKA Moscow v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2012, anh nhanh ch\u00f3ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i gi\u00fap anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp v\u00e0o \u0110TQG Brazil, Fernandes c\u0169ng c\u00f3 1 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho Selecao.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mario Fernandes sang suot khi khoac ao DT Nga\" title=\"Mario Fernandes s\u00e1ng su\u1ed1t khi kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110T Nga\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/toi-di-xem-bong-da.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mario Fernandes s\u00e1ng su\u1ed1t khi kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110T Nga</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u1edbi Dani Alves, \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eafp s\u00e1ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf \u0110TQG, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea5y qu\u1ed1c t\u1ecbch Nga v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2016 v\u00e0 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi v\u00e0o \u0110TQG.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nK\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn nay anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 9 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Nga. \u1ede World Cup 2018 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i. Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Isco.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nR\u00f5 r\u00e0ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u1ea5y qu\u1ed1c t\u1ecbch Nga c\u1ee7a Fernandes t\u1ecf ra h\u1ee3p l\u00fd b\u1edfi anh r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0110T Brazil, ngay c\u1ea3 khi Dani Alves d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 World Cup 2018, nh\u1eefng Fagner ho\u1eb7c Danilo v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua cu\u1ed9c: David De Gea</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o M.U \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n David De Gea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u1edf World Cup 2018, song m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990 l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"De Gea vs Nga\" title=\"De Gea vs Nga\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/Tay-Ban-Nha-bi-loai-La-Roja-be-tac-va-noi-that-vong-De-Gea-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>De Gea g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng to\u00e0n t\u1eadp \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n7 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a&nbsp; \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/de-gea-bi-nhan-mua-gach-da-sau-man-trinh-dien-kho-tin-o-world-cup-2018-421-190143.html\" target=\"_blank\">th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n De Gea</span> \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn 6 l\u1ea7n. M\u1ed9t th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1990.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u00e1ch m\u00f3c HLV Fernando Hierro khi qu\u00e1 \u01b0u \u00e1i De Gea v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Kepa Arrizabalaga. V\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Bilbao, Arrizabalaga x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua cu\u1ed9c: T\u00e2y Ban Nha</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c khi sa th\u1ea3i HLV Julen Lopetegui.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tay Ban Nha co mot ky World Cup that vong\" title=\"T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/171728-tbn.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf B\u00f2 t\u00f3t s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfn qu\u00e1 s\u00e2u \u1edf World Cup 2018 b\u1edfi ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Fernando Hierro ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec9nh cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c. D\u00f9 \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng B nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec T\u00e2y Ban Nha th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c, h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 B\u0110N v\u00e0 Ma R\u1ed1c c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a v\u00e0 nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Iran v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nga, d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, song T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 v\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 3-4 \u1edf lo\u1ea1t s\u00fat lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn th\u1ee9 2 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp T\u00e2y Ban Nha g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf VCK Euro 2016 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Italia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"813","checkdouble":"190192"},{"date":"17:30 02/07","title":"3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin Mexico s\u1ebd ti\u1ec5n Brazil v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1edbm","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/2/3-ly-do-de-tin-mexico-se-tien-brazil-ve-nuoc-som.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau khi m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i, li\u1ec7u Brazil c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng chung s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn v\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c, Argentina hay T\u00e2y Ban Nha. C\u00f3 3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra sau tr\u1eadn Brazil vs Mexico v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay.</h2><h2>1. Mexico r\u1ea5t gi\u1ecfi ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i VCK World Cup n\u0103m nay, \u0110T Mexico \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra c\u00fa s\u1ed1c kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c trong m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn m\u00e0 h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 33%.\u00a0<o:p></o:p>Hirving Lozano \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng d\u00e2n t\u1ed9c c\u1ee7a Mexico khi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, gi\u00e1n ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u01b0a \u2018c\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng \u0110\u1ee9c\u2019 v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1edbm.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Brazil vs Mexico 3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin Mexico s\u1ebd ti\u1ec5n Brazil v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Brazil vs Mexico 3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin Mexico s\u1ebd ti\u1ec5n Brazil v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/Brazil-vs-Mexico-3-ly-do-de-tin-Mexico-se-tien-Brazil-ve-nuoc-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf tr\u1eadn\u00a0Brazil vs Mexico v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay?</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u trong th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn m\u00e0 Mexico ph\u1ea3i ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi El Tri, khi m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t tinh th\u1ea7n quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf b\u1ecb ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u00e9p s\u00e2n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng CONCACAF \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau m\u1ed9t pha ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng s\u1eafc n\u00e9t. \u1ede ph\u00fat 35 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Chicharito t\u1ec9a b\u00f3ng cho Lozano b\u0103ng xu\u1ed1ng tr\u1ed1ng tr\u1ea3i khi Kimmich kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp l\u00f9i v\u1ec1. V\u00e0 sau m\u1ed9t pha ngo\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 22 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 tung c\u00fa s\u00fat hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c v\u00e0o g\u00f3c g\u1ea7n, kh\u00f4ng cho Manuel Neuer c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n thua s\u1edbm khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u00e0o l\u00ean t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xuy\u00ean th\u1ee7ng b\u01b0\u1edbc t\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00e0nh v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n Guillermo Ochoa. N\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Mexico \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ebf n\u00e0o. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu Brazil coi th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eaft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>2. Brazil th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico <o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Mexico d\u0129 nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao b\u1eb1ng Brazil tuy nhi\u00ean trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 El Tri th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean gieo r\u1eafc nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7i \u2018kinh ho\u00e0ng\u2019 cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 x\u1ee9 s\u1edf Samba.\u00a0<o:p></o:p>T\u1ea1i Confed Cup 2005 v\u00e0 Copa America 2007, Mexico \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Brazil d\u00f9 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3 c\u00e1c v\u0169 c\u00f4ng Samba c\u00f3 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea5t h\u00f9ng h\u1eadu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ed7i \u0111au c\u1ee7a Brazil ch\u01b0a d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u00f3. N\u0103m 2012, Brazil mang \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh sang Anh d\u1ef1 Olympic. Trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam, m\u1ed9t Mexico kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao v\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Brazil 2-1 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh HCV k\u1ef3 Olympic 2012, chi\u1ebfc huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 khao kh\u00e1t.\u00a0<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Brazil vs Mexico\" title=\"Brazil vs Mexico\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/brazilmexico2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Brazil th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Mexico</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2001 cho t\u1edbi nay, Mexico \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p Brazil 7 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u0111\u00fang 2 tr\u1eadn. Trong l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i World Cup 2014, Mexico \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 5 l\u1ea7n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00ednh r\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n, \u1edf 15 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng, Mexico th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n gi\u00e0nh \u01b0u th\u1ebf v\u1edbi 7 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 5 l\u1ea7n nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. N\u00f3i v\u1eady \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y, El Tri th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 k\u1ecb d\u01a1 v\u1edbi Selecao v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Tite x\u00e1ch h\u00e0nh l\u00fd v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1edbm.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>3. Ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng Hirving Lozano<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hirving Lozano ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Mexico trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c. Pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c c\u1ee7a ch\u00e0ng trai n\u0103m nay m\u1edbi 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Mexico c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng F.\u00a0<o:p></o:p>S\u1edf h\u1eefu k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Lozano ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean m\u00e0 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Brazil s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p coi th\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lozano ghi ban duy nhat cho Mexico\" title=\"Lozano ghi ban duy nhat cho Mexico\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/liverpool-va-arsenal-dai-chien-vi-sao-moi-noi-o-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Lozano c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u01a1n \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi \u0110T Brazil</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede VCK n\u00e0y, \u0110T Brazil \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng Dani Alves v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, v\u00e0 thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Danilo ho\u1eb7c Fagner. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 hai h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t sau khi d\u00ednh ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u2018g\u00f3t ch\u00e2n Achille\u2019 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Brazil, v\u00e0 th\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng may h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t Hirving Lozano \u0111ang c\u0103ng tr\u00e0n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 khao kh\u00e1t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Mexico. V\u00ec v\u1eady n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn, Brazil r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd \u0111i v\u00e0o \u2018v\u1ebft xe \u0111\u1ed5\u2019 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c sau 90 ph\u00fat trong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u gi\u1eefa Brazil vs Mexico s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:Roboto;color:#261C1C\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/hlv-mexico-lo-so-tot-do-truoc-tran-gap-brazil-469-190186.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/hlv-mexico-lo-so-tot-do-truoc-tran-gap-brazil.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/hlv-mexico-lo-so-tot-do-truoc-tran-gap-brazil-469-190186.html\">HLV Mexico lo s\u1ee3 t\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Brazil</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-brazil-vs-mexico-va-du-doan-soi-keo-mexico-vs-brazil-421-190178.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/nhan-dinh-brazil-vs-mexico-va-du-doan-soi-keo-mexico-vs-brazil.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-brazil-vs-mexico-va-du-doan-soi-keo-mexico-vs-brazil-421-190178.html\">Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng cho c\u1ea7u \u0111inh Brazil vs Mexico</span><br>\r\nNh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs Mexico kh\u00f4ng ai ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u nh\u00e0m ch\u00e1n. Phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn d\u00f9 theo nh\u1eefng phong c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c nhau.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-brazil-vs-mexico-21h-ngay-27-cho-doi-tran-cau-kinh-dien-421-190148.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/nhan-dinh-brazil-vs-mexico-21h-ngay-27-cho-doi-tran-cau-kinh-dien.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-brazil-vs-mexico-21h-ngay-27-cho-doi-tran-cau-kinh-dien-421-190148.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs Mexico (21h ng\u00e0y 2/7): Ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n</span><br>\r\nNh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs Mexico h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd t\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i m\u1edbi bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"812","checkdouble":"190193"},{"date":"09:25 02/07","title":"Su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 Luka Modric n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/messi-chang-phai-la-dang-cuu-the-trong-su-cuong-si-cua-nguoi-ham-mo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Luka Modric ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Croatia, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng 1 qu\u1ea3 11m nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i vui m\u1eebng khi Croatia v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Luka Modric \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng 11m \u1edf hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 th\u1ee9 2</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCroatia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110an M\u1ea1ch 3-2 tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Luka Modric v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0nh cho 8 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luka Modric ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Luka Modric ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/Luka-Modric-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Dan-Mach-vs-Croatia-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Modric b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n \u1edf ph\u00fat 114</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Luka Modric su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a Croatia. Theo \u0111\u00f3, ph\u00fat 114, Croatia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t 11m sau khi Mathias Jorgensen ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi Ante Rebic trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c ch\u1ec9 tay v\u00e0o ch\u1ea5m 11m v\u00e0 Luka Modric b\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00ean ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t, tuy nhi\u00ean anh l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Kasper Schmeichel khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u1ea3i b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u00e1 penalty c\u00e2n n\u00e3o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nR\u1ea5t may cho Modric l\u00e0 Croatia \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng anh s\u1ebd b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ha-dan-mach-vao-tu-ket-hlv-croatia-noi-gi-421-190147.html\" target=\"_blank\">HLV Croatia kh\u00f4ng tr\u00e1ch Modric </span>sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng anh \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng 11m \u1edf cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 th\u1ee9 2.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Luka Modric th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng sau khi \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng 11m</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Luka Modric ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Croatia, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng 1 qu\u1ea3 11m nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i vui m\u1eebng khi Croatia v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luka Modric noi ve tran Dan Mach vs Croatia\" title=\"Luka Modric n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Croatia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/messi-chang-phai-la-dang-cuu-the-trong-su-cuong-si-cua-nguoi-ham-mo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Luka Modric n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Croatia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. T\u00f4i kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3. Tuy nhi\u00ean, chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Croatia l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t, t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Croatia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft ho\u1eb7c th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Nga, h\u1ecd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 \u0111ang ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng Croatia c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"811","checkdouble":"190151"},{"date":"09:16 02/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (1h00 ng\u00e0y 3/7): Li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 th\u00eam \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/nhan-dinh-bi-vs-nhat-ban-1h00-ngay-37-lieu-co-them-dia-chan.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u1edfi ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p gi\u1eefa hai b\u00ean. Nh\u01b0ng trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, ch\u1eb3ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hy v\u1ecdng n\u00e0o cho \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u \u00c1?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">X\u00e9t tr\u00ean l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft, hy v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u \u00c1 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng cao. T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt l\u00e1ch qua khe c\u1eeda h\u1eb9p khi h\u01a1n Senegal v\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 fair-play m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c FIFA \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, B\u1ec9 to\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 ba tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (1h00 ng\u00e0y 37) Li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 th\u00eam \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (1h00 ng\u00e0y 37) Li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 th\u00eam \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/Nhan-dinh-Bi-vs-Nhat-Ban-(1h00-ngay-37)-Lieu-co-them-dia-chan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>C\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u00e0 n\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao nh\u01b0 Hazard, De Bruyne kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t khi ghi 9 b\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 sau 3 tr\u1eadn. S\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u m\u0169i nh\u1ecdn nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u01b0 Hazard, Lukaku, Mertens, De Bruyne. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 h\u00f2a h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 v\u1eady cho \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u0110T B\u1ec9 v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao khi s\u1edf h\u1eefu d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 &quot;th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng&quot;. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u00f4ng l\u1edbn \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Roberto Martinez c\u00e0ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, \u0110T B\u1ec9 v\u1eabn s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c pha b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng v\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Lukaku \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m b\u00e0n. \u0110T Nh\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u1edf nh\u1eefng pha kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn khi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao trung b\u00ecnh th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/3-ly-do-khien-dt-anh-that-bai-truoc-bi-466-189957.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/3-ly-do-khien-dt-anh-that-bai-truoc-bi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/3-ly-do-khien-dt-anh-that-bai-truoc-bi-466-189957.html\">3 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u0110T Anh th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9</span><br>\r\nB\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Adnan Januzaj l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t duy nh\u1ea5t trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Anh v\u00e0 B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00eam qua. \u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n trong khi Anh \u0111\u1ee5ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n cho \u0111\u1ebfn nay ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Colombia nh\u1edd chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf v\u00f4 duy\u00ean ngay \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a Carlos Sanchez, h\u00f2a Senegal khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u01a1i l\u1ecfng \u1edf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Tr\u1eadn thua Ba Lan cho th\u1ea5y Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n l\u1edbn tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u ch\u01a1i k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt v\u00e0 gi\u00e0u toan t\u00ednh.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i World Cup v\u1eabn l\u00e0 v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i. Ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, ch\u01a1i thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 \u0110T B\u1ec9, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c &quot;samurai xanh&quot; kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao.</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng l\u1edbn ng\u00e3 ng\u1ef1a?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 v\u1eady, vi\u1ec7c m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t \u00f4ng l\u1edbn ng\u00e3 ng\u1ef1a t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Akira Nishino c\u00f3 th\u00eam \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c. T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c1 kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, qua \u0111\u00f3 ti\u1ec5n nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0 c\u00fa s\u1ed1c l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Bi vs Nhat Ban\" title=\"Preview B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/Bi-vs-Nhat.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n: \u00d4ng l\u1edbn ng\u00e3 ng\u1ef1a?</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u01b0a d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u00f3, ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga c\u0169ng v\u1eeba t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u1ed1c kh\u00e1c khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ec3 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n tham kh\u1ea3o b\u1edfi c\u1ea3 \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n, ch\u01a1i l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 do \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1ng n\u00ean.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0110T B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ee1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tung \u0111\u00f2n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn:</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i World Cup \u1edf 6/7 l\u1ea7n g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 hai l\u1ea7n g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u00e0o c\u00e1c n\u0103m 1986 v\u00e0 2014.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi trong c\u1ea3 11 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp World Cup, thua 8 (th\u1eafng 2, h\u00f2a 1). Trong s\u1ed1 9 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, \u0110T B\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i k\u00e9o d\u00e0i \u0111\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 trong 5 tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018 (9). H\u1ecd c\u0169ng to\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 ba tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Croatia v\u00e0 Uruguay.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* B\u1ec9 b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong 22 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t (th\u1eafng 17, h\u00f2a 5).&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf 6 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u (th\u1eafng 1, h\u00f2a 2, thua 3).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 World Cup n\u0103m 1998, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u1ee9 c\u00e1ch m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 l\u1ea1i gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng (2002, 2010, 2018) nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd \u0111i xa h\u01a1n v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (1h00 ng\u00e0y 3/7):</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>B\u1ec9 (3-4-2-1): </strong>1.Courtois - 2.Alderweireld, 20.Boyata, 5.Vertonghen - 15.Meunier, 7.De Bruyne, 6.Witsel, 11.Carrasco - 14.Mertens, 10.Hazard - 9.Lukaku</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (4-2-3-1): </strong>1.Kawashima - 19.Sakai, 3.Shoji, 22.Yoshida, 5.Nagatomo - 17.Hasebe, 7.Shibasaki - 8.Haraguchi, 10.Kagawa, 14.Inui - 15.Osako</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1:</strong> B\u1ec9 3-1 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Bi vs Nhat Ban\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/Bi-vs-Nhat-Ban-(3-4-2-1-vs-4-2-3-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-bi-nhm-dang-co-danh-gia-sai-lam-ve-de-bruyne-421-190001.html\">HLV B\u1ec9: NHM \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 sai l\u1ea7m v\u1ec1 De Bruyne</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/alexis-sanchez-dua-ra-du-doan-doi-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-421-189982.html\">Alexis Sanchez \u0111\u01b0a ra d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-bi-nhan-3-tin-mung-truoc-tran-gap-nhat-ban-421-189979.html\">\u0110T B\u1ec9 nh\u1eadn 3 tin m\u1eebng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/3-ly-do-khien-dt-anh-that-bai-truoc-bi-466-189957.html\">3 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u0110T Anh th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/vuot-qua-vong-bang-mot-cach-kho-tin-hlv-nhat-ban-noi-gi-421-189893.html\">V\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch kh\u00f3 tin, HLV Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/keisuke-honda-nguoi-giup-nhat-ban-nuoi-duong-hy-vong-di-tiep-421-189870.html\">Keisuke Honda: Ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u00fap Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n nu\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong> </strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nh\u01b0 \u0110\u1ea1t (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"810","checkdouble":"190153"},{"date":"09:34 02/07","title":"Barca mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u201ckh\u1eafc tinh\u201d c\u1ee7a Messi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/15/barca-muon-mua-kante-cua-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kasper Schmeichel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Croatia, d\u00f9 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp nh\u01b0ng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Leicester v\u1eabn c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kasper Schmeichel ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nR\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng nay, Croatia v\u00e0 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0103n mi\u1ebfng tr\u1ea3 mi\u1ebfng li\u00ean t\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kasper Schmeichel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kasper Schmeichel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/Kasper-Schmeichel-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Dan-Mach-vs-Croatia-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kasper Schmeichel ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kasper Schmeichel c\u1ee7a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, anh c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng pha c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Leicester c\u00f2n c\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 11m c\u1ee7a Modric \u1edf ph\u00fat 114.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, Kasper Schmeichel c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Thua 2-3 tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m penalty c\u00e2n n\u00e3o, \u0110an M\u1ea1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c r\u1eddi World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-croatia-vs-dan-mach-421-190118.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Croatia</span> gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kasper Schmeichel c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o d\u00f9 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kasper Schmeichel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Croatia, d\u00f9 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp nh\u01b0ng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Leicester v\u1eabn c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Schmeichel noi ve tran Dan Mach vs Croatia\" title=\"Schmeichel n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Croatia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/dan-mach-bi-loai-thu-mon-schmeichel-van-cam-thay-tu-hao.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Schmeichel n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Croatia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, nh\u01b0ng \u0110an M\u1ea1ch c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n ng\u1ea9ng cao \u0111\u1ea7u r\u1eddi gi\u1ea3i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c NHM c\u0169ng th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. R\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m x\u00fac v\u00e0o t\u1eeb ng\u1eef v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Croatia, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u1ea3 11m c\u1ee7a Modric, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111i ti\u1ebfp\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"809","checkdouble":"190155"},{"date":"09:55 02/07","title":"\u201cH\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\u201d Barca s\u1eafp c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/marlon-chuan-bi-gia-nhap-southampton.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Marlon chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia nh\u1eadp Southampton. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng t\u1ea1i Barcelona c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn CLB c\u1ee7a Premier League v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Marlon kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng t\u1ea1i Barca</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMarlon t\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 l\u00e0 Marlon Santos da Silva Barbosa, sinh ng\u00e0y 7 th\u00e1ng 9 n\u0103m 1995. Anh chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Barcelona t\u1eeb Fluminense d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a 2016/17. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 t\u1ed1t khi ch\u01a1i cho \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb, trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Blaugrana k\u00fd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh mua \u0111\u1ee9t v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 5 tri\u1ec7u Euro ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng sau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng do kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u00edn nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a HLV m\u1edbi Ernesto Valverde, Barca \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em Marlon cho Nice c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p m\u01b0\u1ee3n trong 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i k\u00e8m \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t 20 tri\u1ec7u Euro h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. C\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Fluminense m\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Marlon chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia nh\u1eadp Southampton t\u1eeb Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Marlon chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia nh\u1eadp Southampton t\u1eeb Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/marlon-chuan-bi-gia-nhap-southampton.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Marlon chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia nh\u1eadp Southampton t\u1eeb Barca</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNice kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Marlon v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3 anh l\u1ea1i Barca tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n. V\u00e0 khi m\u00e0 Valverde v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1edbi Southampton</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ef1c t\u1ebf Marlon c\u0169ng c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p r\u1eddi Barca. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i Premier League n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh l\u00e0 Southampton v\u00e0 West Ham \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 trung v\u1ec7 t\u1eebng c\u00f3 2 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i 1 Blaugrana.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Marlon chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia nh\u1eadp Southampton. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mi\u1ec1n Nam n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 trung v\u1ec7 22 tu\u1ed5i. Trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Marlon s\u1ebd t\u1edbi Southampton ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf, ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a CLB n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Marlon s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a Southampton h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Stuart Armstrong t\u1eeb Celtic v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Basler Mohamed Elyounoussi t\u1eeb Basel. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, The Saints \u0111ang \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft m\u0169i nh\u1ecdn Andrea Petagna c\u1ee7a Atalanta.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-nhan-tin-cuc-mung-vu-sao-barca-172-189954.html\">Liverpool nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c m\u1eebng v\u1ee5 sao Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/rafinha-muon-roi-barca-cang-som-cang-tot-180-189772.html\">Sao Barca tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i c\u00e0ng s\u1edbm c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/barca-muon-so-huu-dong-doi-cua-neymar-sau-world-cup-2018-172-189666.html\">Barca mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Neymar sau World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-bat-ngo-muon-chi-80-trieu-euro-mua-pogba-serbia-180-189646.html\">Barca b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Pogba Serbia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-va-real-dai-chien-vi-sao-bayern-munich-180-189512.html\">Barca v\u00e0 Real \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao Bayern Munich</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"808","checkdouble":"190156"},{"date":"09:51 02/07","title":"M\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \"Pogba Serbia\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/16/mot-doi-bong-tu-choi-co-hoi-chieu-mo-pogba-serbia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Juventus mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00e1n ng\u1ea5y v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi t\u1eeb Lazio.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Juventus quan t\u00e2m Sergej Milinkovic-Savic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJuventus \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin quan t\u00e2m ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Sergej Milinkovic-Savic c\u1ee7a Lazio.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Juventus mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Juventus-mua-Sergej-Milinkovic-Savic-dang-rat-kho-khan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Juventus mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Milinkovic-Savic&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Lazio, anh ghi t\u1edbi 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Serie A. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia h\u1ed9i t\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ee7 nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, anh t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJuventus tin r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Serie A c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Juventus. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/doi-bong-cua-serie-a-bat-ngo-hoi-mua-sao-khung-arsenal-172-189741.html\" target=\"_blank\">Lazio quan t\u00e2m Ramsey</span> c\u1ee7a Arsenal cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 Sergej Milinkovic-Savic ra \u0111i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn t\u1eeb ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i mua Milinkovic-Savic</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Juventus mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00e1n ng\u1ea5y v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi t\u1eeb Lazio.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Milinkovic-Savic\" title=\"Milinkovic-Savic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/9/Lazio-muon-mua-Aaron-Ramsey-thay-Milinkovic-Savic-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u00f2i h\u1ecfi c\u1ee7a Lazio d\u00e0nh cho Milinkovic-Savic khi\u1ebfn Juventus kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, theo Tuttosport, Lazio \u0111\u00f2i 100 tri\u1ec7u euro c\u1ed9ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Rodrigo Bentancur m\u1edbi ch\u1ecbu nh\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i, n\u1ebfu Juventus kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb m\u00e0 Juventus g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng, b\u1edfi v\u1eady h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat lui trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 80 tri\u1ec7u euro m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n MU, PSG v\u00e0 Barca l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i, song s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn m\u00e0 Lazio y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u00e0o c\u1ea3n khi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea1i gia c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u ph\u00e1 k\u00e9t \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Milinkovic-Savic.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"807","checkdouble":"190157"}]}